VitalMatch – Child Safety & Protection Standards (CSAE Policy)

Effective Date: [Insert Date]
Applies to: VitalMatch mobile app and related services

1. Our Commitment to Child Safety

VitalMatch is a peer support platform designed for individuals navigating cancer experiences. We are fully committed to preventing, detecting, and reporting any form of child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE).

We maintain zero tolerance for any content, behavior, or interaction that exploits or endangers minors.

2. Age Requirements

VitalMatch is intended for users 18 years of age or older.

We do not knowingly allow minors to create accounts.

If we become aware that a minor has registered, we will promptly suspend or delete the account.

We may request age verification where appropriate.

3. Prohibited Content and Conduct

The following are strictly prohibited on VitalMatch:

Any sexual content involving minors

Child sexual abuse material (CSAM)

Grooming behavior or solicitation of minors

Sexual exploitation, trafficking, or coercion

Sharing or requesting sexually explicit images of minors

Any attempt to facilitate off-platform abuse

Accounts engaging in such conduct will be permanently banned.

4. Reporting Mechanisms

We provide users with clear tools to report:

Inappropriate messages

Suspicious user behavior

Exploitative or harmful content

Users can report concerns directly within the app or by contacting:

Email: pan.maker.1870@gmail.com

Subject Line: URGENT SAFETY REPORT – VitalMatch

All reports are reviewed promptly and handled with priority.

5. Enforcement & Actions

When CSAE-related content or behavior is identified, VitalMatch will:

Immediately remove offending content

Permanently suspend or ban involved accounts

Preserve relevant records as required

Report confirmed cases to appropriate authorities, including:

The National Center for Missing & Exploited Children (NCMEC) (for U.S. cases)

Other relevant law enforcement agencies as legally required

6. Moderation & Prevention

To maintain a safe environment, VitalMatch implements:

User reporting systems

Account monitoring and moderation review

Clear community guidelines

Rapid escalation protocols for high-risk cases

We continuously improve our safety measures to align with evolving regulatory and platform requirements.

7. Cooperation with Law Enforcement

VitalMatch complies with applicable laws and will cooperate fully with lawful investigations related to child safety.

